SIMPLE: unfriendly
RECORDS: 1

==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Unfriendly
<hw>Un*friend"ly</hw>, <pos>a.</pos> <sn>1.</sn> <def>Not friendly; not
kind or benevolent; hostile; <as>as, an <ex>unfriendly</ex>
neighbor</as>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>Not favorable; not adapted to promote or support any
object; <as>as, weather <ex>unfriendly</ex> to health</as>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p>-- <wordforms><wf>Un*friend"li*ness</wf> <pr>(#)</pr>,
<pos>n.</pos></wordforms>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Unfriendship</ent>⟦br⟧
